    "actor": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment for COU1 is Accepted. The FEA model ensemble demonstrated adequate agreement with experimental data across N=11 constructs at two independent laboratories. All QoI differences were within the pre-established 10% acceptance bound and E/uval values remained below 1.96. Although the Test conditions factor did not achieve the required level due to a single test condition, the model risk level and medium consequence classification support acceptance with acknowledgment of this limitation. The assessment team concludes the model is sufficiently credible for its intended regulatory use.",
